We're looking for a living kid.

00:52:46.771 --> 00:52:48.006
About twelve?

00:52:48.008 --> 00:52:50.507
Have you seen a living boy?

00:52:50.509 --> 00:52:56.129
♪ Un poqui-ti-ti-ti-ti-ti-ti-
