♪ I sing a secret song to
you Each night we are apart

01:13:08.781 --> 01:13:11.146
♪ Remember me

01:13:11.148 --> 01:13:12.481
Papa!

01:13:12.483 --> 01:13:16.835
♪ Though I have to
travel far Remember me

01:13:17.689 --> 01:13:21.625
♪ Each time
